---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Case Studies — Ansh Bhatt"
  description="Real outcomes from real constraints. High-stakes startup consulting results."
>

  <section style="padding:80px 0 64px;border-bottom:1px solid #E8E8E8;">
    <div style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 32px;">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0B3D2E;margin-bottom:16px;">Case Studies</div>
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,50px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.042em;line-height:1.1;color:#0B0B0B;margin:0 0 20px;max-width:560px;">
        Real outcomes.<br/>Real constraints.
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:#5F5F5F;line-height:1.65;max-width:520px;margin:0;">
        Every engagement is custom. Each produces different outputs—but all follow the same framework: clear diagnosis, explicit options, and rigorous execution.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding:72px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #E8E8E8;">
    <div style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 32px;">
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:20px;">

        <div style="background:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #E8E8E8;border-radius:14px;padding:36px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0B3D2E;margin-bottom:14px;">Healthtech</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:#0B0B0B;margin:0 0 24px;line-height:1.3;">Revenue cycle overhaul + product launch support</h3>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;flex:1;">
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5F5F5F;margin-bottom:6px;">Constraint</div>
              <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:#0B0B0B;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">Billing leakage + unclear product-market fit for women's healthtech MVP.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5F5F5F;margin-bottom:6px;">Intervention</div>
              <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:#0B0B0B;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">Streamlined documentation and revenue cycle. Led product from ideation to MVP with funding outreach.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top:auto;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid #E8E8E8;">
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0B3D2E;margin-bottom:6px;">Result</div>
              <p style="font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;color:#0B0B0B;margin:0;">$30K savings + $112K revenue boost. 4 LOIs secured.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #E8E8E8;border-radius:14px;padding:36px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0B3D2E;margin-bottom:14px;">AI / LLM</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:#0B0B0B;margin:0 0 24px;line-height:1.3;">Benefit documentation logic redesign at scale</h3>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;flex:1;">
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5F5F5F;margin-bottom:6px;">Constraint</div>
              <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:#0B0B0B;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">Benefit documentation accuracy issues across a platform serving 80,000 users.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5F5F5F;margin-bottom:6px;">Intervention</div>
              <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:#0B0B0B;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">Led redesign of EOC, DME, and hidden-fee documentation logic within a proprietary LLM system.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top:auto;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid #E8E8E8;">
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0B3D2E;margin-bottom:6px;">Result</div>
              <p style="font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;color:#0B0B0B;margin:0;">NPV improved to 9.8 across benefit documentation workflows.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #E8E8E8;border-radius:14px;padding:36px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0B3D2E;margin-bottom:14px;">Cleantech / PropTech</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:#0B0B0B;margin:0 0 24px;line-height:1.3;">Startup operations + GTM from zero</h3>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;flex:1;">
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5F5F5F;margin-bottom:6px;">Constraint</div>
              <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:#0B0B0B;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">Early-stage startup with no operational infrastructure, no GTM strategy, and no funding.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5F5F5F;margin-bottom:6px;">Intervention</div>
              <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:#0B0B0B;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">Built operations and sales function. Deployed MVP across cleantech, construction, and proptech verticals.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top:auto;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid #E8E8E8;">
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0B3D2E;margin-bottom:6px;">Result</div>
              <p style="font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;color:#0B0B0B;margin:0;">$150K in funding raised. $80K+ in revenue generated.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background:#F6F6F6;border-bottom:1px solid #E8E8E8;padding:56px 0;">
    <div style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 32px;text-align:center;">
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#5F5F5F;line-height:1.7;max-width:580px;margin:0 auto 6px;">
        For confidentiality reasons, most engagements stay private. These represent publicly referenceable outcomes.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#5F5F5F;margin:0;">Ask me directly during an initial call for more detail.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background:#0B3D2E;padding:80px 0;">
    <div style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 32px;text-align:center;">
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(22px,4vw,38px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.1;color:#fff;margin:0 0 16px;">
        Want to talk through your specific situation?
      </h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 36px;">30 minutes. No obligation. Clear next steps.</p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;padding:13px 28px;background:#fff;color:#0B0B0B;border-radius:999px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.01em;text-decoration:none;"
        onmouseover="this.style.opacity='0.88'"
        onmouseout="this.style.opacity='1'"
      >
        Book a call
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
